{"type": "article", "id": 39975, "title": "厨房太小？这套平板式工具能帮你省点地方｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-04-19T23:02:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 39653, "name": "Band Industries"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 154, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170419221343IKcHmb8M04wlXQjL.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Ori-Kit by&nbsp;Amr Aboelnasr &amp;&nbsp;Anas Elshafey</h3><p>当埃及设计师 Amr Aboelnasr 踏入主要由妻子打理的厨房时，他发现各式各样的厨具和餐具虽然能够提供生活上的便利，但它们也在不知不觉间占据了太多的空间。为了让厨房变得精简甚至可以随身携带，他和擅长折纸的艺术家 Anas Elshafey 合作研发了这款名为 Ori-Kit 的平板式工具组，其中包含三种大小的勺子、小铲、漏斗和八边形的过滤器，折叠式的使用方式或许会让你联想到我们之前介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/33313.html\">四合一量勺</a>。这些工具主要由硅胶和特氟龙（Teflon）制成，最高可以承受 260 摄氏度的烹饪温度。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1765747315/ori-kit-replace-your-old-kitchen-tools-with-a-simp\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，套装售价从 30 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221419NfwxYKCGFXZWhvqB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.633824\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221419w80cWCAjZYvNTmkV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221419IQAr2feN6aOG3Vzs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221419UxeTv2Kr1c6lmqn7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.632353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221418wYGsnkliX9fHCRDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Roadie 2 &amp; Roadie Bass by Band Industries</h3><p>2013 年，致力于开发乐器辅助工具的美国公司 Band Industries 推出了第一款智能调音器 Roadie Tuner：只要将它安装在旋钮上，再根据配套 App 中的提示拨动琴弦，它就会自动进行调弦，精确度达到人耳的三倍。最近，设计团队又带来了名为 Roadie 2 的迭代版和低音电吉他专用的 Roadie Bass，新版不仅将适用范围扩大到所有吉他式器乐头的弦乐乐器，还可以在没有手机的情况下完成调弦。除此之外，用户还可以通过 App 储存调弦模式或是查看琴弦的情况，以便及时换弦。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/roadietuner/roadie-2-and-roadie-bass-automatic-instrument-tune\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 89 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221505maXRIrzhGCj9bt6k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669118\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221505MHUoG1y83NtJP96Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704192215055R9XEDst2VlcBMzu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221506h5gQULYj8ZSa4x9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Art &amp; Machine by Ryan Hewlett</h3><p>想了解机器在设计和艺术史中带来的几次重大变革有了更轻松活泼的方式。这套名为 Art &amp; Machine 的扑克牌是美国泰勒艺术学院（Tyler School of Art）艺术研究生 <a href=\"http://ryanhewlett.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ryan Hewlett</a> 的作品，卡面上的插图根据花色分为包豪斯时期的印刷术、中世纪的书籍封面、20 世纪末丝网印刷海报以及移动时代的设计风格四种主题。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221527NrBu8LiKpYMfcX9w.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704192215284qwfdkc7zyOv3sEB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017041922152932VcbQK0eXWtpk5l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704192215278NM4RJHxhGcKuVvW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Universal Hand Dryer by Hyunsu Park</h3><p>你有没有在洗手间内见过因为干手器设置过高，不得不把孩子抱起来的家长或是够不到机器感应范围的残障人士？为了让干手器能够满足所有人的需要，韩国设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/hyunsupark\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hyunsu Park</a> 构思了一款上下都可以出风的干手器，并将它命名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/45915857/Universal-Hand-Dryer\" rel=\"nofollow\">Universal Hand Dryer</a>。内置的探测器保证它只会在监测到用户手势的一端出风，并不会加大电量消耗。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221558RLoqGIBQx5rS2X4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.673333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221600t58wBmFUsjinPIGO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704192215580xepJHCGhl5ya8EL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221558dtfmUPESxXBp6zjR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221558zLaHhuEo1qG7wdF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Dino Ice by Sasha B. Perelman &amp; Katya Mushkina</h3><p>通过吃冰棒，你也可以“解救”恐龙了。这套名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/35954489/DINO-ICE-fruit-ice-lolly\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dino Ice</a> 的冰棒由俄罗斯设计师 Sasha B. Perelman 和 Katya Mushkina 以琥珀为灵感打造，三种水果口味的岩石状冰块将恐龙造型的塑料棍顶端“封印”了起来，配合一半透明一半插画的外包装，让人有一种在北极挖掘恐龙化石的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704192216214V7YUhNcIAiwaD5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.681905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221621ArST4U72ORIY6LHb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221621bRC4Q68OTK7p1Bch.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.627619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704192216217YfuJQBjp6cbOE9a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221621lbys8TxduzwG1DLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.835238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>From MRE to Michelin by Chuck George et al.</h3><p>我们对食物的认知在一定程度上也由它们的摆盘决定，为了改变人们对军用即食口粮（Meals Ready to Eat）的看法，来自纽约的厨师 Chuck George 和录像师 <a href=\"http://jimmypham.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jimmy Pham</a> 以及摄影师 <a href=\"http://henryhargreaves.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Henry Hargreaves</a> 联手创作了这套名为 From MRE to Michelin 的作品。在收集了来自各个国家的口粮之后，George 参照米其林星级餐厅中的摆盘方式将它们汇集成一道道精致的菜肴。作为一名军人的儿子，George 也希望通过这种形式向军队的餐饮文化表示尊重，并且满足人们对于这种食物的好奇心。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221738buBstT1oS4RInN3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221738WgCb8ErK1a6UIMeH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221740neE3Tlt1qzHvNDMV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221739RkPheAzl7nvMECLt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221739xlri8SWYkhzVLU0v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419221738FEKnSMcGd1V7bwe2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}